metadata.name: Brutalist #215
metadata.description:
from the depth
the architect ponder
reshape my world
in hollow order

#11
experimental vintage series

press "C" to turn on/off outlines
press "V" to turn on/off background objects and grid, if any present
press "B" to turn on/off rotation
press "N" to reload with different layout, 3 iterations to cycle through

press "UP arrow" to increase render scale multiplier by x1 (maximum is x4, default is x3)
press "DOWN arrow" to decrease render scale multiplier by x1 (minimum is x1)

press "S" to save png in live view

metadata.name: Impending Cloths #27
metadata.description:
IC makes use of fabric's potential for contrasts.
The same piece of cloth can seem to be falling, perfectly still and ready to be blown away, all at the same time.
It can look "very digital" while also achieving a high degree of texture. And so on, and so forth. Contrast and potential.
Also, "h" can be pressed to download in high resolution, although it may take up to a minute.
